snippet.title: Guacamelee! - Gameplay - PS3
snippet.description:
You can also check out my review for Guacamelee! here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lmIhwyNbre8

Guacamelee! developed by Drinkbox Studios lets you take the role of Juan who becomes a luchador. Punch and fight through baddies while traversing through the world in this action platform game on the PS3/PSV.

You can also check out my review for Guacamelee! here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lmIhwyNbre8


Add me on PSN: Omegabalmung

Subscribe if you like my videos: http://www.youtube.com/user/Omegabalmung99?feature=mhee
